<div class="returnRefundPolicy">
  <div class="returnRefundPolicyTitle">
    <p>Return & Refund Policy</p>
  </div>

  <p>Your will be responsible for paying for your own shipping costs for returning your item. Shipping costs are non-refundable.</p>
  
  <div>
    <p>For Quality Related Reason</p>
    <p><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0556/1253/9040/files/returnRefundPolicyImg1.jpg?v=1642841743" width="60%" alt=""></p>
  </div>
  
