      <li>The item(s) must have been purchased from www.nakto.com</li>
      <li>Returns will be accepted within 14 days of purchase</li>
      <li>The item(s) must be in new, unused condition with original packaging</li>
      <li>Proof of purchase required. </li>
    </ul>
