  </div>

  <div>
    <p>Return to Nakto Warehouse</p>
    <p>Bring your order, with proof of purchase, to our warehouse at </p>
    <p>1683 Sierra Madre Circle, Placentia, <br>CA 92870, USA</p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <p>Return by Mail</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Email us at support@nakto.com with description of your situation, your order number and date of purchase</li>
      <li>Pack the item(s) in the original packaging and ship them back to 1683 Sierra Madre Circle, Placentia, CA 92870, USA</li>
      <li>Once your return package has arrived at our warehouse, please allow 3-4 business days for us to process your refund.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>


</div>





